   - File System Desync: If a file is deleted from the uploads/ folder but remains in the assets metadata (or vice versa), the UI will throw 404s.

  4. Latency Potential
   - Cold Start AI: Every analyze call initializes a new Gemini request. Sequential analysis of 5+ files creates a "Latency Stack" (File Read -> AI Analysis -> Summary Generation).
